# Validation Contract

- Label claims: `runtime-verified`, `static-only`, or `speculative`.
- Never state speculative outcomes as facts.
- Runtime-impacting work must report: commands run, outcomes, and unverified items.
- If runtime checks were not run, say so directly.

# Safety Boundaries

- Docs/workflow passes do not modify gameplay runtime logic.
- Keep low-mutation lanes non-speculative unless explicitly escalated.

